    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is a total dream! This beauty is in pristine, mint condition and has been babied since the day I got her. Always garage-kept, non-smoker, and it honestly still has that new-car feel. It drives incredibly smooth and looks showroom-ready. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and well-maintained, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
