      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving Bavarian engineering, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system. The mechanical integrity of this specimen is absolute; the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with VAC-coated shells, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with TMS plates to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and tactile feedback. The exterior finish remains in showroom condition, free of rock chips or clear coat failure, while the interior maintains its factory matte texture. This is a turnkey, collector-grade vehicle optimized for the purist who values linear power delivery and telepathic chassis response.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
