    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed since day one. The exterior boasts a flawless, deep-luster finish with absolutely no swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather still retains its factory scent, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented by the dealership and zero leaks or unusual noises. It comes complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
