      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen features a documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with factory-spec precision. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the chassis remains free of oxidation. With zero deferred maintenance and optimal compression across all cylinders, this vehicle offers the raw, mechanical purity that defined the golden era of M-division engineering.",
